{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":760,"text":"What keeps us healthy and happy"},{"time":3760,"text":"as we go through life?"},{"time":6520,"text":"If you were going to invest now"},{"time":9040,"text":"in your future best self,"},{"time":11120,"text":"where would you put your time\nand your energy?"},{"time":15120,"text":"There was a recent survey of millennials"},{"time":17560,"text":"asking them what their\nmost important life goals were,"},{"time":22760,"text":"and over 80 percent said"},{"time":24800,"text":"that a major life goal for them\nwas to get rich."},{"time":28960,"text":"And another 50 percent\nof those same young adults"},{"time":33320,"text":"said that another major life goal"},{"time":35880,"text":"was to become famous."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38960,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":40200,"text":"And we're constantly told\nto lean in to work, to push harder"},{"time":46880,"text":"and achieve more."},{"time":48960,"text":"We're given the impression that these\nare the things that we need to go after"},{"time":52640,"text":"in order to have a good life."},{"time":54480,"text":"Pictures of entire lives,"},{"time":56720,"text":"of the choices that people make\nand how those choices work out for them,"},{"time":61960,"text":"those pictures\nare almost impossible to get."},{"time":66080,"text":"Most of what we know about human life"},{"time":69160,"text":"we know from asking people\nto remember the past,"},{"time":72640,"text":"and as we know, hindsight\nis anything but 20/20."},{"time":77440,"text":"We forget vast amounts\nof what happens to us in life,"},{"time":81160,"text":"and sometimes memory\nis downright creative."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84800,"text":"But what if we could watch entire lives"},{"time":89200,"text":"as they unfold through time?"},{"time":92080,"text":"What if we could study people\nfrom the time that they were teenagers"},{"time":96080,"text":"all the way into old age"},{"time":98840,"text":"to see what really keeps people\nhappy and healthy?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":103560,"text":"We did that."},{"time":105640,"text":"The Harvard Study of Adult Development"},{"time":107880,"text":"may be the longest study\nof adult life that's ever been done."},{"time":113720,"text":"For 75 years, we've tracked\nthe lives of 724 men,"},{"time":121360,"text":"year after year, asking about their work,\ntheir home lives, their health,"},{"time":125880,"text":"and of course asking all along the way\nwithout knowing how their life stories"},{"time":130280,"text":"were going to turn out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133280,"text":"Studies like this are exceedingly rare."},{"time":136920,"text":"Almost all projects of this kind\nfall apart within a decade"},{"time":141000,"text":"because too many people\ndrop out of the study,"},{"time":144200,"text":"or funding for the research dries up,"},{"time":147120,"text":"or the researchers get distracted,"},{"time":149400,"text":"or they die, and nobody moves the ball\nfurther down the field."},{"time":154280,"text":"But through a combination of luck"},{"time":156560,"text":"and the persistence\nof several generations of researchers,"},{"time":160280,"text":"this study has survived."},{"time":162520,"text":"About 60 of our original 724 men"},{"time":167040,"text":"are still alive,"},{"time":168360,"text":"still participating in the study,"},{"time":170560,"text":"most of them in their 90s."},{"time":173560,"text":"And we are now beginning to study"},{"time":175480,"text":"the more than 2,000 children of these men."},{"time":179680,"text":"And I'm the fourth director of the study."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183400,"text":"Since 1938, we've tracked the lives\nof two groups of men."},{"time":188160,"text":"The first group started in the study"},{"time":190320,"text":"when they were sophomores\nat Harvard College."},{"time":193040,"text":"They all finished college\nduring World War II,"},{"time":195880,"text":"and then most went off\nto serve in the war."},{"time":199280,"text":"And the second group that we've followed"},{"time":201440,"text":"was a group of boys\nfrom Boston's poorest neighborhoods,"},{"time":205640,"text":"boys who were chosen for the study"},{"time":207680,"text":"specifically because they were\nfrom some of the most troubled"},{"time":211040,"text":"and disadvantaged families"},{"time":212920,"text":"in the Boston of the 1930s."},{"time":215680,"text":"Most lived in tenements,\nmany without hot and cold running water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222520,"text":"When they entered the study,"},{"time":224440,"text":"all of these teenagers were interviewed."},{"time":227400,"text":"They were given medical exams."},{"time":229640,"text":"We went to their homes\nand we interviewed their parents."},{"time":233200,"text":"And then these teenagers\ngrew up into adults"},{"time":235600,"text":"who entered all walks of life."},{"time":238040,"text":"They became factory workers and lawyers\nand bricklayers and doctors,"},{"time":244160,"text":"one President of the United States."},{"time":248160,"text":"Some developed alcoholism.\nA few developed schizophrenia."},{"time":253320,"text":"Some climbed the social ladder"},{"time":255640,"text":"from the bottom\nall the way to the very top,"},{"time":258880,"text":"and some made that journey\nin the opposite direction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263520,"text":"The founders of this study"},{"time":266480,"text":"would never in their wildest dreams"},{"time":268520,"text":"have imagined that I would be\nstanding here today, 75 years later,"},{"time":273080,"text":"telling you that\nthe study still continues."},{"time":277280,"text":"Every two years, our patient\nand dedicated research staff"},{"time":280920,"text":"calls up our men\nand asks them if we can send them"},{"time":284000,"text":"yet one more set of questions\nabout their lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":288040,"text":"Many of the inner city Boston men ask us,"},{"time":291640,"text":"\"Why do you keep wanting to study me?\nMy life just isn't that interesting.\""},{"time":296600,"text":"The Harvard men never ask that question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":308920,"text":"To get the clearest picture\nof these lives,"},{"time":311800,"text":"we don't just send them questionnaires."},{"time":314760,"text":"We interview them in their living rooms."},{"time":317240,"text":"We get their medical records\nfrom their doctors."},{"time":320200,"text":"We draw their blood, we scan their brains,"},{"time":322720,"text":"we talk to their children."},{"time":324440,"text":"We videotape them talking with their wives\nabout their deepest concerns."},{"time":329720,"text":"And when, about a decade ago,\nwe finally asked the wives"},{"time":333280,"text":"if they would join us\nas members of the study,"},{"time":335680,"text":"many of the women said,\n\"You know, it's about time.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":338400,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":339480,"text":"So what have we learned?"},{"time":341200,"text":"What are the lessons that come\nfrom the tens of thousands of pages"},{"time":346440,"text":"of information that we've generated"},{"time":349520,"text":"on these lives?"},{"time":351720,"text":"Well, the lessons aren't about wealth\nor fame or working harder and harder."},{"time":358520,"text":"The clearest message that we get\nfrom this 75-year study is this:"},{"time":364840,"text":"Good relationships keep us\nhappier and healthier. Period."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371000,"text":"We've learned three big lessons\nabout relationships."},{"time":374840,"text":"The first is that social connections\nare really good for us,"},{"time":378960,"text":"and that loneliness kills."},{"time":381480,"text":"It turns out that people\nwho are more socially connected"},{"time":385160,"text":"to family, to friends, to community,"},{"time":388280,"text":"are happier, they're physically healthier,\nand they live longer"},{"time":393000,"text":"than people who are less well connected."},{"time":396400,"text":"And the experience of loneliness\nturns out to be toxic."},{"time":399840,"text":"People who are more isolated\nthan they want to be from others"},{"time":405000,"text":"find that they are less happy,"},{"time":408240,"text":"their health declines earlier in midlife,"},{"time":411200,"text":"their brain functioning declines sooner"},{"time":413440,"text":"and they live shorter lives\nthan people who are not lonely."},{"time":418040,"text":"And the sad fact\nis that at any given time,"},{"time":421280,"text":"more than one in five Americans\nwill report that they're lonely."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427040,"text":"And we know that you\ncan be lonely in a crowd"},{"time":429720,"text":"and you can be lonely in a marriage,"},{"time":432400,"text":"so the second big lesson that we learned"},{"time":434560,"text":"is that it's not just\nthe number of friends you have,"},{"time":437680,"text":"and it's not whether or not\nyou're in a committed relationship,"},{"time":441200,"text":"but it's the quality\nof your close relationships that matters."},{"time":446560,"text":"It turns out that living in the midst\nof conflict is really bad for our health."},{"time":451360,"text":"High-conflict marriages, for example,\nwithout much affection,"},{"time":455360,"text":"turn out to be very bad for our health,\nperhaps worse than getting divorced."},{"time":461160,"text":"And living in the midst of good,\nwarm relationships is protective."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465960,"text":"Once we had followed our men\nall the way into their 80s,"},{"time":469080,"text":"we wanted to look back at them at midlife"},{"time":472120,"text":"and to see if we could predict"},{"time":473720,"text":"who was going to grow\ninto a happy, healthy octogenarian"},{"time":477720,"text":"and who wasn't."},{"time":479680,"text":"And when we gathered together\neverything we knew about them"},{"time":483920,"text":"at age 50,"},{"time":486080,"text":"it wasn't their middle age\ncholesterol levels"},{"time":488640,"text":"that predicted how they\nwere going to grow old."},{"time":491560,"text":"It was how satisfied they were\nin their relationships."},{"time":495040,"text":"The people who were the most satisfied\nin their relationships at age 50"},{"time":499960,"text":"were the healthiest at age 80."},{"time":503680,"text":"And good, close relationships\nseem to buffer us"},{"time":506880,"text":"from some of the slings and arrows\nof getting old."},{"time":510480,"text":"Our most happily partnered men and women"},{"time":514480,"text":"reported, in their 80s,"},{"time":516559,"text":"that on the days\nwhen they had more physical pain,"},{"time":519520,"text":"their mood stayed just as happy."},{"time":522400,"text":"But the people who were\nin unhappy relationships,"},{"time":525680,"text":"on the days when they\nreported more physical pain,"},{"time":528640,"text":"it was magnified by more emotional pain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":532360,"text":"And the third big lesson that we learned\nabout relationships and our health"},{"time":536760,"text":"is that good relationships\ndon't just protect our bodies,"},{"time":540040,"text":"they protect our brains."},{"time":542440,"text":"It turns out that being\nin a securely attached relationship"},{"time":547120,"text":"to another person in your 80s\nis protective,"},{"time":551040,"text":"that the people who are in relationships"},{"time":553040,"text":"where they really feel they can count\non the other person in times of need,"},{"time":557200,"text":"those people's memories\nstay sharper longer."},{"time":560920,"text":"And the people in relationships"},{"time":562440,"text":"where they feel they really\ncan't count on the other one,"},{"time":565600,"text":"those are the people who experience\nearlier memory decline."},{"time":570520,"text":"And those good relationships,\nthey don't have to be smooth all the time."},{"time":574000,"text":"Some of our octogenarian couples\ncould bicker with each other"},{"time":577600,"text":"day in and day out,"},{"time":579360,"text":"but as long as they felt that they\ncould really count on the other"},{"time":582560,"text":"when the going got tough,"},{"time":584400,"text":"those arguments didn't take a toll\non their memories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589600,"text":"So this message,"},{"time":592360,"text":"that good, close relationships\nare good for our health and well-being,"},{"time":598080,"text":"this is wisdom that's as old as the hills."},{"time":601040,"text":"Why is this so hard to get\nand so easy to ignore?"},{"time":605560,"text":"Well, we're human."},{"time":607040,"text":"What we'd really like is a quick fix,"},{"time":609880,"text":"something we can get"},{"time":611600,"text":"that'll make our lives good\nand keep them that way."},{"time":615320,"text":"Relationships are messy\nand they're complicated"},{"time":618680,"text":"and the hard work of tending\nto family and friends,"},{"time":622520,"text":"it's not sexy or glamorous."},{"time":625200,"text":"It's also lifelong. It never ends."},{"time":628560,"text":"The people in our 75-year study\nwho were the happiest in retirement"},{"time":633640,"text":"were the people who had actively worked\nto replace workmates with new playmates."},{"time":639480,"text":"Just like the millennials\nin that recent survey,"},{"time":642480,"text":"many of our men when they\nwere starting out as young adults"},{"time":646120,"text":"really believed that fame and wealth\nand high achievement"},{"time":650160,"text":"were what they needed to go after\nto have a good life."},{"time":654120,"text":"But over and over, over these 75 years,\nour study has shown"},{"time":658320,"text":"that the people who fared the best were\nthe people who leaned in to relationships,"},{"time":664000,"text":"with family, with friends, with community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":669080,"text":"So what about you?"},{"time":671080,"text":"Let's say you're 25,\nor you're 40, or you're 60."},{"time":675800,"text":"What might leaning in\nto relationships even look like?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":679760,"text":"Well, the possibilities\nare practically endless."},{"time":683600,"text":"It might be something as simple\nas replacing screen time with people time"},{"time":689720,"text":"or livening up a stale relationship\nby doing something new together,"},{"time":694200,"text":"long walks or date nights,"},{"time":697360,"text":"or reaching out to that family member\nwho you haven't spoken to in years,"},{"time":702240,"text":"because those all-too-common family feuds"},{"time":705760,"text":"take a terrible toll"},{"time":708000,"text":"on the people who hold the grudges."}]},{"cues":[{"time":712000,"text":"I'd like to close with a quote\nfrom Mark Twain."},{"time":717280,"text":"More than a century ago,"},{"time":719680,"text":"he was looking back on his life,"},{"time":722320,"text":"and he wrote this:"},{"time":724840,"text":"\"There isn't time, so brief is life,"},{"time":728560,"text":"for bickerings, apologies,\nheartburnings, callings to account."},{"time":734720,"text":"There is only time for loving,"},{"time":737560,"text":"and but an instant,\nso to speak, for that.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":742760,"text":"The good life is built\nwith good relationships."}]},{"cues":[{"time":747160,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":748400,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}